dc_title_s: Ann Arbor, Michigan; drawn & published by A. Ruger.
dc_description_s: Bird's-eye view. Relief shown by shading. "Chicago Lithographing Co." Oriented with north to the upper right. Includes index to points of interest and 10 ill. 1 view: hand col.; 46 x 72 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
